{"tid":1146105,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《Anthem》前路茫茫，重要開發人員相繼離開","createTime":"2019-05-09T04:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T05:02:50.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c78706d94913859490369836fc5f112f2fb79aa5","tid":1146105,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:59:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.gameapps.hk/news/33297/Anthem-Dragon-Age\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gameapps.hk%2Fnews%2F33297%2FAnthem-Dragon-Age&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYV7Oh%2FyAFRgp1rU3tL1w%2BGY%3D&h=08b0d0d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gameapps.hk/news/33297/Anthem-Dragon-Age</a><br />\n<br />\n《Anthem》的開發公司 BioWare 近日已經將旗下部分員工調離《Anthem》的崗位，並轉移至下一隻重點開發遊戲《闇龍紀元》(Dragon Age) 新作，再引發一些玩家不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201905/06/rRQpPbArPfBsejBL2CcuP3-970-80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201905%2F06%2FrRQpPbArPfBsejBL2CcuP3-970-80.jpg&h=bf30b460&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然一隻遊戲在正式推出後，公司把開發人員崗位進行調配，開發一些新作也是十分正常的事，不過在玩家眼中，《Anthem》的情況就不是這樣了，因為這還稱不上是「完成」的遊戲，最近部分《Anthem》的重點開發人員已經調離崗位，轉移開發《闇龍紀元》新作了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Nw3lrXlti-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNw3lrXlti-8&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYV7Oh%2FyAFRgp1rU3tL1w%2BGY%3D&h=86f4a0cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Nw3lrXlti-8</a>"},{"pid":"3695a0806276b53d63b8385555e665945eb07952","tid":1146105,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T05:02:50.000Z","msg":"人員調度引發玩家批評後，官方並未針對此次的事件發佈相關的正式聲明，不過其高層人員 Chad Robertson 已在個人推特上強調 BioWare 的立場未變，依然是全力支持《冒險聖歌》的後續開發，也相當期待遊戲未來的更新內容，但也不敢做過多的承諾，會等到整體內容接近完工的狀態後再進行展示。不過基於《冒險聖歌》開發團隊至今的種種表現和事故來看，要平息玩家的不安與不滿，恐怕還不太夠。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gbc.tw/gb_img/s300q80/3898269l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gbc.tw%2Fgb_img%2Fs300q80%2F3898269l.jpg&h=50258155&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gamebase.com.tw/news/topic/99186104/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamebase.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ftopic%2F99186104%2F&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYV7Oh%2FyAFRgp1rU3tL1w%2BGY%3D&h=131e28cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gamebase.com.tw/news/topic/99186104/</a>"}]}